  "identifier": "HB 69",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to housing and declaring an emergency.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 198A, relating to affordable housing, to define terms; require agencies that expend state or federal affordable housing funds to expend at least 90% of those funds on single-family detached housing and no more than 10% of those funds on multifamily housing in any given fiscal year; EMERGENCY.",
